No. 09-627. Rick Thaler, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division, Petitioner v. Eric Lynn Moore. 559 U.S. 998, 130 S. Ct. 1736,

176 L. Ed. 2d 222,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 2238. March 8, 2010.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 342 Fed. Appx. 65.
